            UK/EU future relationship draft document - what's in it?
            The EU and UK have set out a draft agreement on their future relationship, paving the way for a potential Brexit deal.The document outlines how trade, security and other issues will work - and the European Council says it has been "agreed in principle". Adam Fleming has had a look at what's in it.
                
